o]]\n* Dante Gonzalgo\n* [[Rudy Distrito]]\n* Dondon Ampalayo\n* Pido Jarencio\n* [[Manny Victorino]]\n* Sonny Cabatu\n* Jayvee Gayoso\n* Noli Locsin\n* Bal David\n* Marlou Aquino\n* EJ Feihl\n{{column}}\n* Vince Hizon\n* Wilmer Ong\n* Vergel Meneses\n* Jun Limpot\n* Ronald Magtulis\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* Eric Menk\n* Mark Caguioa\n* Jayjay Helterbrand\n* Rommel Adducul\n* Sunday Salvacion\n* Ronald Tubid\n* Junthy Valenzuela\n* David Noel\n* Paul Artadi\n* Cyrus Baguio\n* Willie Miller\n* Rudy Hatfield\n* JC Intal\n* Dylan Ababou\n* Rico Maierhofer\n* LA Tenorio\n* Chris Ellis\n* Japeth Aguilar\n* Greg Slaughter\n* Mac Baracael\n* Joe Devance\n* Scottie Thompson \n* Kevin Ferrer\n{{columns-end}}\n|}\n\n===PBA Press Corps Awardee===\n{| class=wikitable\n|-\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San Miguel}}\" width=\"33%\" | PBA Press Corps'Danny Floro Executive of the Year\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San Miguel}}\" width=\"33%\" | PBA Press Corps' Coach of the Year\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San Miguel}}\" width=\"33%\" | PBA Press Corps' Finals MVP\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* Robert Non- 2012-2013\n* Henry Cojuangco- 2004-2005\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* Jong Uichico&nbsp;\u2013 2006\u20132007\n* Siot Tanquingcen&nbsp;\u2013 2004\u20132005\n* Robert Jaworski Sr.&nbsp;\u2013 1988\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* LA Tenorio - 2016 Governor's Cup, 2017 Governors' Cup\n* Ronald Tubid&nbsp;\u2013 2008 Fiesta Conference (co-MVP)\n* Jayjay Helterbrand&nbsp;\u2013 2006\u20132007 Philippine Cup\n* Eric Menk&nbsp;\u2013 2008 Fiesta Conference (co-MVP), 2004\u20132005 Philippine Cup, 2004 Fiesta Conference\n* Marlou Aquino&nbsp;\u2013 1997 Commissioner's Cup\n|-\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San Miguel}}\" width=\"33%\" | PBA Press Corps' Defensive Player of the Year\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San Miguel}}\" width=\"33%\" | PBA Press Corps' Comeback Player of the Year\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San M