h)&nbsp;\u2013 2005, 2007\n* Vergel Meneses (Veterans)&nbsp;\u2013 2000\n* Bal David (RSJ)&nbsp;\u2013 1997\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* Robert Labagala&nbsp;\u2013 2011\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* Robert Jaworski - 1990, 1996\n|-\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San Miguel}}\" width=\"33%\" | PBA All Star Coach\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San Miguel}}\" width=\"33%\" | PBA Greats vs PBA Stalwarts Game Selection\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San Miguel}}\" width=\"33%\" | PBA Rookies vs Sophomores Blitz Game Selection\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* Robert Jaworski - 1990, 1991, 1992, 1996, 1997\n* Allan Caidic - 2001\n* Jong Uichico - 2007\n* Tim Cone - 2017\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* Leo Isaac\n* Jayjay Helterbrand\n* KG Canaleta\n* Mike Cortez\n* Noli Locsin\n* Vince Hizon\n* Rodney Santos\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* Mark Macapagal\n* Mike Holper\n* Chris Pacana\n* John Wilson\n* Robert Labagala\n|-\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San Miguel}}\" width=\"33%\" | PBA All&nbsp;\u2013 Star Challenge Events Champions\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San Miguel}}\" width=\"33%\" colspan=\"2\"| PBA ALL Star Selection\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* Marlou Aquino&nbsp;\u2014 Slam Dunk - 1996\n* Noli Locsin&nbsp;\u2014 Slam Dunk - 1996\n* Tyrone Hopkins (import) - Slam Dunk - 1997\n* Mike Orquillas&nbsp;\u2014 Slam Dunk - 1997\n* Bal David&nbsp;\u2013 Buzzer Beater&nbsp;\u2013 1999\n* Edward Naron&nbsp;\u2014 Buzzer Beater - 2000\n* Jayjay Helterbrand&nbsp;\u2014 Buzzer Beater - 2001\n* Aris Dimaunahan&nbsp;\u2013 2 Ball Challenge&nbsp;\u2013 2003\n* Sunday Salvacion&nbsp;\u2013 2 Ball Challenge&nbsp;\u2013 2003\n* Jayjay Helterbrand&nbsp;\u2013 Shooting Star Challenge&nbsp;\u2013 2007\n* Paul Artadi&nbsp;\u2013 Obstacle Challenge&nbsp;\u2013 2009\n* David Noel&nbsp;\u2013 Slam Dunk (Import)&nbsp;\u2013 2009\n* David Noel&nbsp;\u2013 Slam Dunk (Dunk-off)&nbsp;\u2013 2009\n* Ronald Tubid&nbsp;\u2014 Legends Shootout - 2011\n* KG Canaleta&nbsp;\u2013 Slam Dunk&nbsp;\u2013 2012\n* Chris Ellis&nbsp;\u2014 Slam Dunk - 2012-2013\n| valign=\"top\" |\n{{columns-start|num=2}}\n* Robert Jaworski\n* Chito Loyzaga\n* Joey Loyzaga\n* Philip Cezar\n* [[Rey Cuenco]]\n* Dante Gonzalgo\n* [[Rudy Distrito]]\n* Dondon Ampalayo\n* Pido Jarencio\n* [[Manny Victorino]]\n* Sonny Cabatu\n* Jayvee Gayoso\n* Noli Locsin\n* Bal David\n* Marlou Aquino\n* EJ Feihl\n{{column}}\n* Vince Hizon\n* Wilmer Ong\n* Vergel Meneses\n* Jun Limpot\n* Ronald Magtulis\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* Eric Menk\n* Mark Caguioa\n* Jayjay Helterbrand\n* Rommel Adducul\n* Sunday Salvacion\n* Ronald Tubid\n* Junthy Valenzuela\n* David Noel\n* Paul Artadi\n* Cyrus Baguio\n* Willie Miller\n* Rudy Hatfield\n* JC Intal\n* Dylan Ababou\n* Rico Maierhofer\n* LA Tenorio\n* Chris Ellis\n* Japeth Aguilar\n* Greg Slaughter\n* Mac Baracael\n* Joe Devance\n* Scottie Thompson \n* Kevin Ferrer\n{{columns-end}}\n|}\n\n===PBA Press Corps Awardee===\n{| class=wikitable\n|-\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San Miguel}}\" width=\"33%\" | PBA Press Corps'Danny Floro Executive of the Year\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San Miguel}}\" width=\"33%\" | PBA Press Corps' Coach of the Year\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San Miguel}}\" width=\"33%\" | PBA Press Corps' Finals MVP\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* Robert Non- 2012-2013\n* Henry Cojuangco- 2004-2005\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* Jong Uichico&nbsp;\u2013 2006\u20132007\n* Siot Tanquingcen&nbsp;\u2013 2004\u20132005\n* Robert Jaworski Sr.&nbsp;\u2013 1988\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* LA Tenorio - 2016 Governor's Cup, 2017 Governors' Cup\n* Ronald Tubid&nbsp;\u2013 2008 Fiesta Conference (co-MVP)\n* Jayjay Helterbrand&nbsp;\u2013 2006\u20132007 Philippine Cup\n* Eric Menk&nbsp;\u2013 2008 Fiesta Conference (co-MVP), 2004\u20132005 Philippine Cup, 2004 Fiesta Conference\n* Marlou Aquino&nbsp;\u2013 1997 Commissioner's Cup\n|-\n! style=\"{{PBA color cell|Barangay Ginebra San Miguel}}\" width=\"33%\" 